~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

   The Linux Zorro Utilities contain a utility for dealing with the Zorro bus
in Linux:

	- lszorro: displays detailed information about all Zorro devices in the
	  system, replacing the original /proc/zorro interface.

   See manual pages for more details.

   If you have any bug reports or suggestions, send them to the author.

   Many IDs were obtained from ExpName/Identify ((C) Richard Körber) and by
   looking at the NetBSD-Amiga kernel sources.

